From d029ac71649116405ac276eb5d49e3b4ff5e1e52 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Tue, 23 Jun 2026 15:20:08 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix(android): replace corrupt gradle-wrapper.jar + add
 .gitattributes

The gradle-wrapper.jar was corrupt in git repository (committed with
text mode line-ending normalization, breaking the binary jar file).
This caused 'Invalid or corrupt jarfile' error in GitHub Actions CI.

Fix:
1. Replace with valid gradle-wrapper.jar (43764 bytes, verified with unzip -t)
2. Add .gitattributes to mark *.jar as binary (prevent future corruption)

Verified: jar integrity test passes (No errors detected)
---
 .gitattributes                            |  22 ++++++++++++++++++++++
 android/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar | Bin 74059 -> 43764 bytes
 2 files changed, 22 insertions(+)
 create mode 100644 .gitattributes

diff --git a/.gitattributes b/.gitattributes
new file mode 100644
index 0000000..65aa90f
--- /dev/null
+++ b/.gitattributes
@@ -0,0 +1,22 @@
+# Auto-detect text files
+* text=auto
+
+# Binary files - never normalize line endings
+*.jar binary
+*.png binary
+*.jpg binary
+*.jpeg binary
+*.gif binary
+*.ico binary
+*.webp binary
+*.woff binary
+*.woff2 binary
+*.ttf binary
+*.otf binary
+*.eot binary
+*.so binary
+*.dex binary
+*.apk binary
+*.aab binary
+*.keystore binary
+*.jks binary
diff --git a/android/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar b/android/gradle/wrapper/gradle-wrapper.jar
index 7c9efe49ea98744186810ad1f8b38787c3b9b4f6..1b33c55baabb587c669f562ae36f953de2481846 100644
GIT binary patch
